{"tid":1695810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有手足將啲popo濫權片整理晒","createTime":"2019-11-06T00:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T07:49:23.000Z","uid":97654,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"6bbd3f0105de3df6837d6701b6319332c9cb5f08","tid":1695810,"uid":97654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T00:41:58.000Z","msg":"利申唔係我<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/mobile/folders/1sdbhvxkWSvbECROtK1XXB8HR-s94vrKG?fbclid=IwAR3Ry7YEgzdFss7xzvfy7xc3yEGFN3GUDQxKTik3Wwj8foK7vQnCsxnTWKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Fmobile%2Ffolders%2F1sdbhvxkWSvbECROtK1XXB8HR-s94vrKG%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3Ry7YEgzdFss7xzvfy7xc3yEGFN3GUDQxKTik3Wwj8foK7vQnCsxnTWKs&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=9cd4166f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/mobile/folders/1sdbhvxkWSvbECROtK1XXB8HR-s94vrKG?fbclid=IwAR3Ry7YEgzdFss7xzvfy7xc3yEGFN3GUDQxKTik3Wwj8foK7vQnCsxnTWKs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［全部同我廣傳］話說，報告出街後，一直有人擔心我地個報告既片源會隨住時間會俾ＦＢ　ＤＥＬ晒。<br />\n好彩我地條ＢＡＣＫＵＰ　ＴＥＡＭ（好似得一條友）係海外已經盡量將Ｄ片一邊做一邊拷貝左。依家見佢已經公開左咁我都唔怕貼出黎。大家如果都想做ＢＡＣＫＵＰ就自己鍾意ＤＬ幾多就幾多啦。有Ｄ可能都未及放落個報告度。但證據就係證據。上千條都唔出奇。<br />\n（我今朝問番美國人原來呢個係另一個片庫，同我地果個片庫唔同係另一個黎，sorry for the confusion)<br />\n連結：<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1sdbhvxkWSvbECROtK1XXB8HR-s94vrKG?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1sdbhvxkWSvbECROtK1XXB8HR-s94vrKG%3F&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=2a67bf77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1sdbhvxkWSvbECROtK1XXB8HR-s94vrKG?</a><br />\n＊＊＊<br />\n報告全文網頁版：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkpfreport.org/full-report\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkpfreport.org%2Ffull-report&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=e4550dfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkpfreport.org/full-report</a><br />\n英文PDF：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/.../1pUkCW08HzHoQXdhZ98OFgM.../view?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2F...%2F1pUkCW08HzHoQXdhZ98OFgM...%2Fview%3F&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=a9fdbb5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/.../1pUkCW08HzHoQXdhZ98OFgM.../view?</a><br />\n中文PDF：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/.../1inNJvVvb7XqEvGLvp3KqZ1.../view?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2F...%2F1inNJvVvb7XqEvGLvp3KqZ1...%2Fview%3F&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=e58930f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/.../1inNJvVvb7XqEvGLvp3KqZ1.../view?</a><br />\nTWITTER推文宣請入:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ellan_ou/status/1183998271074660352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fellan_ou%2Fstatus%2F1183998271074660352&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=7bb39e04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fellan_ou%2Fstatus%2F1183998271074660352&h=f4110d84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ellan_ou/status/1183998271074660352</a><br />\n中文版本&mdash;公眾試閱版&mdash;正文：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/32iru94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32iru94&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=6e35d22b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/32iru94</a><br />\n警隊涉嫌濫權資料（六／七月）：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/31ciO2E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F31ciO2E&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=70bc5198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/31ciO2E</a><br />\n警隊涉嫌濫權資料（至八月十日）：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2IU8ZQB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IU8ZQB&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=9c38c4af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2IU8ZQB</a><br />\n英文版本&mdash;